{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/make/robot/artificial-muscle","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"electromagnets\" style=\"position:relative;\">Electromagnets<a href=\"#electromagnets\" aria-label=\"electromagnets permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.adafruit.com/product/3873\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">electromagnet</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/itm/264599173470\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">solenoid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://learn.adafruit.com/wireless-inductive-power-night-light\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">wireless charging</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"soft-robotics\" style=\"position:relative;\">Soft robotics<a href=\"#soft-robotics\" aria-label=\"soft robotics permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Interesting topic called <a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/epdf/10.1002/adma.202170145\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Soft robotics</a>. Shape changing, regenerating</p>\n<p>Instead of a spring you can use a <a href=\"https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.1246906\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">fishing line</a> (Science, 21 Feb 2014, Vol 343, Issue 6173, pp. 868-872).\nJust twist the fishing line and will swirl into thin spring. If you apply heat it will contract. If you wind up a copper whire around the fishing line first then it can dissipate heat when electricity is applied to the wire.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Illustration <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i8mjU3i3QWE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i8mjU3i3QWE</a></li>\n<li>How to twist <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UbvNW7ONiTc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UbvNW7ONiTc</a></li>\n<li>All together as one arm <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i8mjU3i3QWE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i8mjU3i3QWE</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"pneumatic-muscle-actuators\" style=\"position:relative;\">Pneumatic muscle actuators<a href=\"#pneumatic-muscle-actuators\" aria-label=\"pneumatic muscle actuators permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Tetrahedral locomotion - three legs-tentacles and a neck, but it can swap them interchangeably <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qAkJws7VEcI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qAkJws7VEcI</a></li>\n<li>Soft quadruped <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i8mjU3i3QWE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">video</a>, <a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/10160006\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">article</a></li>\n<li>Tetrahedral kinematics explained <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2303.05454.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2303.05454.pdf</a></li>\n<li>3D print molds for silicone, connect air tubes (see <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iwQRYzLZvGE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">some steps in the video</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://softroboticstoolkit.com/book/pam-fabrication\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">PAM fabrication with pictures</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Pump</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wHYL4cFTAY0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wHYL4cFTAY0</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"memory-alloy-actuator\" style=\"position:relative;\">Memory alloy actuator<a href=\"#memory-alloy-actuator\" aria-label=\"memory alloy actuator permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Just watch videos for <a href=\"https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/scirobotics.aau7557\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">this article</a>: <strong>Chasing biomimetic locomotion speeds: Creating untethered soft robots with shape memory alloy actuators</strong></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"Electromagnets electromagnet solenoid wireless charging Soft robotics Interesting topic called Soft robotics. Shape changing, regenerating…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#electromagnets\">Electromagnets</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#soft-robotics\">Soft robotics</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#pneumatic-muscle-actuators\">Pneumatic muscle actuators</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#memory-alloy-actuator\">Memory alloy actuator</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"date":"July 18, 2023","published":"July 18, 2023","lastModified":"July 18, 2023","title":"Artificial muscle","subtitle":null,"section":null,"draft":null,"developing":null,"buttonText":null,"buttonLink":null,"secondButtonText":null,"secondButtonLink":null,"featuredImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"showLikes":true,"absolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasan.github.io/mikolasan.github.io/src/markdown/make/robot/artificial-muscle.md","url":"/make/robot/artificial-muscle","next":{"excerpt":"What eco-friendly robot differs from others? Such robots can use renewable or alternative sources of energy, such as solar power, biofuel…","fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasan.github.io/mikolasan.github.io/src/markdown/make/robot/eco-friendly.md","frontmatter":{"title":"Eco friendly robot","date":"2023-08-03T00:00:00.000Z","topic":true,"article":null},"id":"b1